.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-FORWARDING-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-forwarding-stats \- aggregate forwarding statistics over a time window
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-forwarding-stats
.RB [ --days
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Counts settled forwards and sums routed volume and fees earned within
the last
.I N
days (default 30).
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{period_days, count, total_in_msat, total_fee_msat}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-api-forward-stats (1),
.BR lightning-node-fee-revenue (1)
